So when you first launch the app

00:11:31.816 --> 00:11:33.336 A:middle
you select movements that you

00:11:33.336 --> 00:11:34.666 A:middle
want to do, these exercise

00:11:34.666 --> 00:11:37.006 A:middle
movements on a screen like this.

00:11:37.396 --> 00:11:38.576 A:middle
And there's dozens of these

00:11:38.576 --> 00:11:38.876 A:middle
things.

00:11:38.876 --> 00:11:40.216 A:middle
You can scroll down and pick as

00:11:40.216 --> 00:11:41.056 A:middle
many as you want.

00:11:42.196 --> 00:11:43.656 A:middle
After that when you want to

00:11:43.656 --> 00:11:45.186 A:middle
start a workout there's just one

00:11:46.406 --> 00:11:46.706 A:middle
tap.

00:11:46.706 --> 00:11:48.346 A:middle
You just pick a duration and you

00:11:48.346 --> 00:11:48.676 A:middle
go.

00:11:49.286 --> 00:11:50.856 A:middle
And the app does the rest.

00:11:51.126 --> 00:11:52.586 A:middle
It auto selects from your

00:11:52.586 --> 00:11:53.946 A:middle
movements and it picks a

00:11:53.946 --> 00:11:56.106 A:middle
sequence and then you're in the

