feel by introducing a sense of

00:12:35.416 --> 00:12:37.876 A:middle
randomness and removing work.

00:12:39.166 --> 00:12:40.886 A:middle
So the developers recognize that

00:12:40.886 --> 00:12:42.906 A:middle
each step in the process of

00:12:42.906 --> 00:12:44.826 A:middle
doing a workout requires a

00:12:44.826 --> 00:12:47.126 A:middle
choice, requires someone to

00:12:47.126 --> 00:12:49.336 A:middle
think about what they want and

00:12:49.336 --> 00:12:51.646 A:middle
these decisions are not things

00:12:51.646 --> 00:12:52.906 A:middle
that everyone wants to make.

00:12:53.806 --> 00:12:55.316 A:middle
So you only choose movements

00:12:55.316 --> 00:12:55.906 A:middle
once.

